properties.Name: HouseholdType
properties.Description:
A domestic unit that consists of members of a family who live together along with non-relatives.

Ex:
-  Family of origination
-  Family of procreation
-  Family
-  Married couple
-  Married couple with children
-  Family No Spouse
-  Male Householder
-  Male Householder with Related Children
-  Female Householder
-  Female Householder with Related Children
-  Nonfamily household
-  One Person Household Male
-  One Person Household Female
-  Two + Persons Male Householder
-  Two + Persons Female Householder
